{"tid":370643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！澳門一街曱甴！","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T01:05:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f60ea4289bac9efa0d62ee4170e407da1d1775","tid":370643,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"受強風吹襲，大自然界昆蟲聞風而逃。有網民稱拍攝得數以萬計的曱甴列隊爬上海旁邊的石壆搬家，片段畫面令人雞皮疙瘩。有眼利網民一眼認出地點是澳門的筷子基住宅屋苑，又叮嚀膽小或女士們勿看！有網民說，看畢影片連男人亦驚「小強」，亦有人笑言「睇動物大遷徙唔使去非洲」丶「好想去瘋狂噴殺蟲水」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有網民於近中午12時，在漁民群組上載水浸相片，指地點為澳門。相中有數艘漁船停泊岸邊，有私家車疑擔心被洪流沖走，用繩索圍繞車身，繫上船隻。10號風球下，到處都是奇聞異象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/photo/bkn-20170823125410963-0823_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170823140243\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170823%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170823125410963-0823_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170823140243&h=b7878373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/bkn-20170823125410963-0823_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028828d47a586180147b9d91fc92b98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170823%2Fbkn-20170823125410963-0823_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D4028828d47a586180147b9d91fc92b98&d=nO9b1a1YD2by4zN8IxcPMpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2d973555\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170823/bkn-20170823125410963-0823_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028828d47a586180147b9d91fc92b98</a>"},{"pid":"058d7ecaa8b18b16c049f694d7ac21db5ab29c87","tid":370643,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04787d0aa0b6af87